Package: montyhall
Title: Running the Monty Hall Game
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Rachel",
           family = "Judd",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "first.last@example.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package runs the Monty Hall game show where contestants have a chance to win a new car by selecting one of three doors. One door has a car behind it and the other two have goats. The game is created using functions and running loops to play multiple times.
Depends: dplyr
